{"tid":2347514,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"其實大逃殺類嘅電影電視劇有咩咁好睇","createTime":"2020-12-31T06:08:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-31T14:08:17.000Z","uid":80481,"like":3,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"2463b40bd59a834dc2e88d53131936eb95b06ca9","tid":2347514,"uid":80481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T06:08:28.000Z","msg":"呢類影視通常都係有個極度強大嘅幕後黑手，將主角同其他二打六韞喺個神秘空間入面。喺空間入面個boss掌控一切，用盡各種手段等主角團鬼打鬼，將佢哋玩弄於股掌間，主角練到再勁對boss來講都只係嗰啲一掌拍得死嘅螻蟻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，就算喺一眾人中殺出血路都只不過係得到幫boss做狗，助紂為虐去虐待新人<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。其實點解啲人咁鍾意睇呢類受虐嘅片<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都係鍾意睇返啲主角可以同boss鬥吓嘅、甚至反殺boss嘅片多啲（好似The Cabin in the Woods嗰啲？）"},{"pid":"f9f25b0dd36ee732fe00340c73030657f8f719c9","tid":2347514,"uid":134620,"like":18,"dislike":2,"score":16,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T06:11:08.000Z","msg":"點解你要管埋人地觀賞喜好?"},{"pid":"8c98832878bae97620d94ec5b3e0605097cba1d6","tid":2347514,"uid":118709,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T06:13:01.000Z","msg":"睇人仆街最開心"},{"pid":"006dd186463f5175e8a82fee0e210d7547ca7d5f","tid":2347514,"uid":4780,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T06:13:02.000Z","msg":"其實主角可以同boss鬥吓嘅、甚至反殺boss嘅片（好似The Cabin in the Woods嗰啲） 有咩咁好睇"},{"pid":"8f28890ca78724b95f0162532a14e1a271c7ce5f","tid":2347514,"uid":80481,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"f9f25b0dd36ee732fe00340c73030657f8f719c9","tid":2347514,"uid":134620,"like":18,"dislike":2,"score":16,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T06:11:08.000Z","msg":"點解你要管埋人地觀賞喜好?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T06:14:21.000Z","msg":"因為睇呢類嘢好似見到香港嘅影子，boss操控所有人鬼打鬼互相殘殺，打贏就幫boss做狗，永遠無得翻身擺脫boss"},{"pid":"11280f7c0eb086bbd75b339384ec2d61