k<br />\n要睇係睇佢內涵 想表達d乜 睇人物塑造<br />\n正如林夕好多情歌 但唔會話佢咁多情歌有咩好聽<br />\n首首唔同 有d講埋佛學<br />\n咪就係睇呢d 洗咩咁介意係咪大逃殺"},{"pid":"523de29cfc977eab1d971338a3130f1bb4704bcb","tid":2347514,"uid":60977,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T06:33:27.000Z","msg":"咁你要睇下深作欣二套大逃殺"},{"pid":"28bfbe3e639869f637e546c1364984a5840f87fa","tid":2347514,"uid":331590,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T06:42:11.000Z","msg":"大逃殺小說or漫畫好睇"},{"pid":"ab57c82fd01cb8466cea7d6d738fc75988b7ab2a","tid":2347514,"uid":60500,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"523de29cfc977eab1d971338a3130f1bb4704bcb","tid":2347514,"uid":60977,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T06:33:27.000Z","msg":"咁你要睇下深作欣二套大逃殺"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T08:36:23.000Z","msg":"電影第2集我覺得好垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cf38e7a2c557412145a7776eedfce461b04e63a","tid":2347514,"uid":11185,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T12:05:50.000Z","msg":"最泯滅人性既逆境之中點樣堅持自己原則、信念、道德"},{"pid":"6c187ebf5bf9343c8dc40199d71f12ca2919249b","tid":2347514,"uid":157092,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"11280f7c0eb086bbd75b339384ec2d616c2957ff","tid":2347514,"uid":266702,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"f9f25b0dd36ee732fe00340c73030657f8f719c9","tid":2347514,"uid":134620,"like":18,"dislike":2,"score":16,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T06:11:08.000Z","msg":"點解你要管埋人地觀賞喜好?"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T06:15:40.000Z","msg":"逢紅必反 多人討論既野 就會話唔明有咩好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />動畫漫畫劇都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T14:08:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大逃殺類嘅戲逢紅必反嘅話樓主都遲左7-8年啦"}]}